ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 22nd day of June, 2006 the above-captioned Petition for Allowance of Appeal, the Petition to Retain Jurisdiction and Allow “Iwanicki” to Seek PCRA Relief and Exhaustion of State Remedies, and the Application for Evidentiary Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
